# Lean build artifacts
/.lake/

# Literature for the box (read off-disk via bind-mount; never redistributed in git).
# Per KB "never commit PDFs to eventually-public repos": keep PDFs local, commit only
# papers/SOURCES.md (the tracked catalog + provenance + summaries).
papers/**/*.pdf
papers/**/*.djvu
papers/**/*.ps

